data.description: This home is situated on a large "L" shaped lot with access from E 8th St as well as Kayser St. It features front, rear and side yards. The current Owner has completed some repairs. All disclosures are available in attached documents.  Entry into the living room is from the covered patio.  The enclosed porch is just off the living room and allows access to the fenced in yard.  One step up into the formal dining room with built ins..   A large rear deck is conveniently located beyond the dining area of the updated, eat-in kitchen.  The  primary bedroom and full bath are nestled  on this level, as well as the laundry & utility rooms.  The loft above the laundry area provides additional storage space. 3 bedrooms and a full bath on the 2nd floor complete this home.  Buyer inspections are for Buyer info only.  Buyer responsible for paying all transfer tax and obtaining C O. Corporate addendums generated with accepted offer.***Best & Final offers due by 10 AM on 12/01/2023***
